431       *
432       * @param item
433       *          the item to add
434       * @return {@code true}
435       */
436      public boolean addProp(Property item) {
437        Property value = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(item, "item cannot be null");
438        if (_props == null) {
439          _props = new LinkedList<>();

451       */
452      public boolean removeProp(Property item) {
453        Property value = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(item, "item cannot be null");
454        return _props != null && _props.remove(value);
455      }

478        _remarks = value;
479      }

482      public String toString() {
483        return new ReflectionToStringBuilder(this, ToStringStyle.MULTI_LINE_STYLE).toString();
484      }
